  "text": "Although we have identified late N1 enhancement in response to auditory stimuli in the present study, Wang et al. [CITATION_1] report a similar enhancement of the N1 elicited following presentation of somatosensory stimuli, raising the possibility that this effect may reflect modulation that is common across different sensory systems.",
